    DOWNBASE:0 += 50
    DOWNBASE:기력 += 80
ELSEIF EXP:긴박경험 < EXPLV:4
    DOWNBASE:0 += 40
    DOWNBASE:기력 += 60
ELSE
    DOWNBASE:0 += 30
    DOWNBASE:기력 += 50
ENDIF

;ABL:마조끼를 본다
